measurements.description: One hundred flowers on 18 up to 15-cm inflorescences and seven buds on three immature inflorescences; 91-cm x 50-cm plant grown in 34-cm plastic pot; sepals and petals lanceolate, white overlaid light mauve; lip tubular, white overlaid light mauve, dark purple distally; column white, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte; also awarded #20245280 CCE.
